      <link>https://longbiosci.com/news/Pragmatism-Preclinical-Aging-Research-NatureAging-2026.html</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://longbiosci.com/news/Pragmatism-Preclinical-Aging-Research-NatureAging-2026.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[Nature Aging发表Steven N. Austad署名文章，指出当前衰老与长寿临床前研究存在系统性方法论缺陷，呼吁采用更务实的研究设计，提高从实验室到临床的可转化性。]]></description>
