      <link>https://longbiosci.com/news/Nucleic-Acid-Mislocalization-Coagul-Aging-Review-2026.html</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://longbiosci.com/news/Nucleic-Acid-Mislocalization-Coagul-Aging-Review-2026.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[最新开放获取综述揭示：衰老细胞中错位的DNA/RNA片段激活cGAS-STING等天然免疫受体，驱动慢性炎症和血栓倾向（coagul-aging），提出核酸可作为衰老干预的潜在靶点。]]></description>
